		site O41    x 0.76592       y 0.76592       z 0.76592       occ O    0.5        beq = boverall;:1.86126`
		
 		scale scale3  6.07454771e-08` min 1e-14 max 1.e+14
		MVW(mass3  1644.397, vol3  741.218`,perc3  0.259`)
		prm scaleZMV3 = scale3 * mass3 * vol3 ;:0.0740399826`
		r_bragg  2.49527134
		LVol_FWHM_CS_G_L(1, 82.3573477`, 0.89, 78.3201296`, csgc3, 88.4527145` min 30 max 9999, !cslc3, 9999)
		e0_from_Strain( 2.18166283e-06`, !sgc3, 0.001, slc3, 1.00072433e-09` min 1e-9 max 0.1)
  
	str  
		phase_name trigonal-ZrMo2O8
