		MVW(mass4  2466.595, vol4  1073.150`,perc4  0.470`)
		prm scaleZMV4 = scale4 * mass4 * vol4 ;:0.134345322`
		r_bragg  2.07925925
		LVol_FWHM_CS_G_L(1, 28.5014305`, 0.89, 27.0363151`, csgc4, 30.4324782` min 30 max 9999, !cslc4, 9999)
